name: Yatsu Murasaki (八津紫) from taimanin (対魔忍)
description:
Murasaki is one of my favorite game characters in action taimanin, her hit reaction animation is amazing when she attacks.

About this LoRA:

I tried to modify some settings in order to facilitate the reduction of the size of the lora, and it works well!

I also trained two different outfits for murasaki, Use the keyword bodysuit to generate her standard outfit, and the keyword gymsuit to generate her sportswear!

Unlike usual, this time i trained this lora by anything 4.5, and it works perfectly with abyssorangemix2_nsfw, perfectworld, and Grapefruit hentai model!

Because of some overtraining of this Lora, I suggest to reduce its weight slightly, 0.4-0.7 would be a good interval.
